<div class="c650_4">
<div id="v650.4.1"><span class="G5399 s">Let us</span><span class="G3767 s"> therefore</span><span class="G5399 s"> fear</span><span class="G3379 s">, lest</span><span class="G1860 s">, a promise</span><span class="G2641 s"> being left</span><span class="G1525 s"> <i>us</i> of entering</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G846 s"> his</span><span class="G2663 s"> rest</span><span class="G5100 s">, any</span><span class="G1537 s"> of</span><span class="G5216 s"> you</span><span class="G1380 s"> should seem</span><span class="G5302 s"> to come short of it</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.2"><span class="G2532 s">For</span><span class="G2070 s"> G1063 unto us was</span><span class="G2097 s"> the gospel preached</span><span class="G2509 s">, as well as</span><span class="G2548 s"> unto them</span><span class="G235 s">: but</span><span class="G3056 s"> the word</span><span class="G189 s"> preached</span><span class="G5623 s"> did</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G5623 s"> profit</span><span class="G1565 s"> them</span><span class="G3361 s">, not</span><span class="G4786 s"> being mixed</span><span class="G4102 s"> with faith</span><span class="G191 s"> in them that heard</span> <i>it</i>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (the word…: Gr. the word of hearing) (not being…: or, because they were not united by faith to)</span></div>
<div id="v650.4.3"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G3588 s"> we which</span><span class="G4100 s"> have believed</span><span class="G1525 s"> do enter</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G2663 s"> rest</span><span class="G2531 s">, as</span><span class="G2046 s"> he said</span><span class="G5613 s">, As</span><span class="G3660 s"> I have sworn</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G3450 s"> my</span><span class="G3709 s"> wrath</span><span class="G1487 s">, if</span><span class="G1525 s"> they shall enter</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G3450 s"> my</span><span class="G2663 s"> rest</span><span class="G2543 s">: although</span><span class="G2041 s"> the works</span><span class="G1096 s"> were finished</span><span class="G575 s"> from</span><span class="G2602 s"> the foundation</span><span class="G2889 s"> of the world</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.4"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G2046 s"> he spake</span><span class="G4225 s"> in a certain place</span><span class="G4012 s"> of</span><span class="G1442 s"> the seventh</span><span class="G3779 s"> <i>day</i> on this wise</span><span class="G2532 s">, And</span><span class="G2316 s"> God</span><span class="G2664 s"> did rest</span><span class="G1722 s"> the seventh</span><span class="G2250 s"> G1442 day</span><span class="G575 s"> from</span><span class="G3956 s"> all</span><span class="G846 s"> his</span><span class="G2041 s"> works</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.5"><span class="G2532 s">And</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G5129 s"> this</span><span class="G3825 s"> <i>place</i> again</span><span class="G1487 s">, If</span><span class="G1525 s"> they shall enter</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G3450 s"> my</span><span class="G2663 s"> rest</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.6"><span class="G1893 s">Seeing</span><span class="G3767 s"> therefore</span><span class="G620 s"> it remaineth</span><span class="G5100 s"> that some</span><span class="G1525 s"> must enter</span><span class="G1519 s"> therein</span><span class="G2532 s"> G846, and</span><span class="G4386 s"> they to whom it was first</span><span class="G2097 s"> preached</span><span class="G1525 s"> entered</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G1525 s"> in</span><span class="G1223 s"> because</span><span class="G543 s"> of unbelief</span>: <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (it was: or, the gospel was)</span></div>
<div id="v650.4.7"><span class="G3825 s">Again</span><span class="G3724 s">, he limiteth</span><span class="G5100 s"> a certain</span><span class="G2250 s"> day</span><span class="G3004 s">, saying</span><span class="G1722 s"> in</span><span class="G1138 s"> David</span><span class="G4594 s">, To day</span><span class="G3326 s">, after</span><span class="G5118 s"> so long</span><span class="G5550 s"> a time</span><span class="G2531 s">; as</span><span class="G2046 s"> it is said</span><span class="G4594 s">, To day</span><span class="G1437 s"> if</span><span class="G191 s"> ye will hear</span><span class="G846 s"> his</span><span class="G5456 s"> voice</span><span class="G4645 s">, harden</span><span class="G3361 s"> not</span><span class="G5216 s"> your</span><span class="G2588 s"> hearts</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.8"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G1487 s"> if</span><span class="G2424 s"> Jesus</span><span class="G2664 s"> had given</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G2664 s"> rest</span><span class="G302 s">, then would he</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G3326 s"> afterward</span><span class="G2980 s"> G5023 have spoken</span><span class="G4012 s"> of</span><span class="G243 s"> another</span><span class="G2250 s"> day</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (Jesus: that is, Joshua)</span></div>
<div id="v650.4.9"><span class="G620 s">There remaineth</span><span class="G686 s"> therefore</span><span class="G4520 s"> a rest</span><span class="G2992 s"> to the people</span><span class="G2316 s"> of God</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (rest: or, keeping of a sabbath)</span></div>
<div id="v650.4.10"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G1525 s"> he that is entered</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G846 s"> his</span><span class="G2663 s"> rest</span><span class="G846 s">, he</span><span class="G2532 s"> also</span><span class="G2664 s"> hath ceased</span><span class="G575 s"> from</span><span class="G846 s"> his own</span><span class="G2041 s"> works</span><span class="G5618 s">, as</span><span class="G2316 s"> God</span><span class="G575 s"> <i>did</i> from</span><span class="G2398 s"> his</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.11"><span class="G4704 s">Let us labour</span><span class="G3767 s"> therefore</span><span class="G1525 s"> to enter</span><span class="G1519 s"> into</span><span class="G1565 s"> that</span><span class="G2663 s"> rest</span><span class="G3363 s">, lest</span><span class="G5100 s"> any man</span><span class="G4098 s"> fall</span><span class="G1722 s"> after</span><span class="G846 s"> the same</span><span class="G5262 s"> example</span><span class="G543 s"> of unbelief</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (unbelief: or, disobedience)</span></div>
<div id="v650.4.12"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G3056 s"> the word</span><span class="G2316 s"> of God</span><span class="G2198 s"> <i>is</i> quick</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G1756 s"> powerful</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G5114 s"> sharper</span><span class="G5228 s"> than</span><span class="G3956 s"> any</span><span class="G1366 s"> twoedged</span><span class="G3162 s"> sword</span><span class="G1338 s">, piercing</span><span class="G891 s"> even to</span><span class="G3311 s"> the dividing asunder</span><span class="G5590 s"> of soul</span><span class="G5037 s"> and</span><span class="G4151 s"> G2532 spirit</span><span class="G5037 s">, and</span><span class="G719 s"> G2532 of the joints</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G3452 s"> marrow</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G2924 s"> <i>is</i> a discerner</span><span class="G1761 s"> of the thoughts</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G1771 s"> intents</span><span class="G2588 s"> of the heart</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.13"><span class="G2532 s">Neither</span><span class="G2076 s"> G3756 is there</span><span class="G2937 s"> any creature</span><span class="G852 s"> that is not manifest</span><span class="G846 s"> in his</span><span class="G1799 s"> sight</span><span class="G1161 s">: but</span><span class="G3956 s"> all things</span><span class="G1131 s"> <i>are</i> naked</span><span class="G2532 s"> and</span><span class="G5136 s"> opened</span><span class="G3788 s"> unto the eyes</span><span class="G846 s"> of him</span><span class="G4314 s"> with</span><span class="G3739 s"> whom</span><span class="G2254 s"> we have</span><span class="G3056 s"> to do</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.14"><span class="G2192 s">Seeing</span><span class="G3767 s"> then</span><span class="G2192 s"> that we have</span><span class="G3173 s"> a great</span><span class="G749 s"> high priest</span><span class="G1330 s">, that is passed into</span><span class="G3772 s"> the heavens</span><span class="G2424 s">, Jesus</span><span class="G5207 s"> the Son</span><span class="G2316 s"> of God</span><span class="G2902 s">, let us hold fast</span><span class="G3671 s"> <i>our</i> profession</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.15"><span class="G1063 s">For</span><span class="G2192 s"> we have</span><span class="G3756 s"> not</span><span class="G749 s"> an high priest</span><span class="G3361 s"> which cannot</span><span class="G4834 s"> G1410 be touched with the feeling</span><span class="G2257 s"> of our</span><span class="G769 s"> infirmities</span><span class="G1161 s">; but</span><span class="G3985 s"> was</span><span class="G2596 s"> in</span><span class="G3956 s"> all points</span><span class="G3985 s"> tempted</span><span class="G2596 s"> G3987 like</span><span class="G3665 s"> as</span><span class="G5565 s"> <i>we are, yet</i> without</span><span class="G266 s"> sin</span>.</div>
<div id="v650.4.16"><span class="G4334 s">Let us</span><span class="G3767 s"> therefore</span><span class="G4334 s"> come</span><span class="G3326 s"> boldly</span><span class="G2362 s"> G3954 unto the throne</span><span class="G5485 s"> of grace</span><span class="G2443 s">, that</span><span class="G2983 s"> we may obtain</span><span class="G1656 s"> mercy</span><span class="G2532 s">, and</span><span class="G2147 s"> find</span><span class="G5485 s"> grace</span><span class="G996 s"> to help</span><span class="G1519 s"> in</span><span class="G2121 s"> time of need</span>.</div></div>
